extractions.description: The study evaluates the quality of direct-to-consumer teleconsultation platforms across Quebec, Ontario, and British Columbia, using a modified version of the HONcode principles.

type.justification: The paper presents an empirical study as it assesses real-world teleconsultation services and provides data and analysis regarding their quality.
type.quote: The objective of this study was to describe and assess the quality of the direct-to-consumer medical teleconsultation landscape in three Canadian provinces.
